                                                                 "label":  "Company Profile: Castleton Partners",
                                                                 "v":  "320 employees, financial services.\nVoluntary turnover: 28% (industry average: 17%)\nEngagement survey eNPS: +12 (industry average: +24)\nPay positioning: market 60th percentile (above median)\n\nExit interview themes, ranked by frequency:\n1. “No clear path to promotion”\n2. “My manager rarely acknowledges good work”\n3. “Workload during close periods is unsustainable”\n4. “Pay is fine, just not exciting”"
